channel.description:

I am unable to login to my Server. The client said: "You need a members account to login to this world. Please subscribe, or use a different world" and on my server side,: [IMG]http://i678.photobucket.com/albums/vv150/mightybean/error.jpg[/img] I dont know where the problem lies. Can you please tell me where is the problem and how can I solve this. Please help me.
Regards,
